## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Build paper
cd paper && make all
```

## Project Structure

```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}/
├── vault/           # Obsidian knowledge base
│   ├── Experiments/ # Experiment notes
│   ├── Literature/  # Paper summaries
│   ├── Reference/   # Data dictionary, methods
│   └── Logs/        # Session logs
├── paper/           # Academic manuscript
│   ├── paper.md     # Main paper
│   ├── supplement.md
│   └── overview.md
├── features/        # Extracted features
├── results/         # Analysis outputs
│   └── figures/     # Publication figures
└── .claude/         # Claude Code config
```

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `vault/Home.md` | Project dashboard |
| `paper/paper.md` | Main manuscript |
| `paper/references.bib` | Bibliography |
| `CLAUDE.md` | AI assistant guidelines |

## Commands

```bash
# Build documents
cd paper && make docx       # Main paper
cd paper && make supplement # Supplementary material
cd paper && make overview   # Technical overview
cd paper && make all        # Build all

# Validate citations
cd paper && make check

# Word count
cd paper && make wordcount
```

## Requirements

- Python 3.9+
- Pandoc 2.19+
- python-docx (`pip install python-docx`)
- Obsidian (optional, for vault editing)

